        bio: 'I focus on making things easier for our clients. Whether I am tackling a complex concern or coordinating with our team behind the scenes, my goal is always the same: to turn technical updates into helpful, straightforward advice. I coordinate with our SEO team to ensure that client requests and feedback are implemented into our processes.',
